    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Requirements</strong> You are wearing your magitek armor, or piloting your magitek mech</p><hr /><p>You electrify your invention to punish foes who dare to attack you. For 1 round, any creature that touches you or your mech, or that hits you or your mech with a melee unarmed attack or a non-reach melee weapon attack, takes @Damage[1d4[electricity]|overrideTraits] damage. The effect ends if you cease wearing your armor innovation or cease piloting your magitek mech.</p><p>If you have the revolutionary invention class feature, the damage increases to 2d4.</p><p><strong>Overcharge Function</strong> You create an unstable chain reaction, sending countless sparks dancing across your armor or mech. Add the amp and overcharge traits to Electrification. The effects last for 1 minute instead of 1 round, and the damage dice increase from d4s to d12s.</p>",
